com.penthera.virtuososdk.client.subscriptions

Class SubscriptionKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.penthera.virtuososdk.client.subscriptions.SubscriptionKey
  • public final class SubscriptionKey extends java.lang.Object
    Specifies the Keys that are used within the Subscription Service. Clients implementing a Subscription Service use these keys to provide the correct meta data to the SDK in their overridden SubscriptionsService.processingFeedWithData(String,JSONObject,boolean) and SubscriptionsService.processingAssetWithData(String,JSONObject,boolean) methods.
    See Also:
    SubscriptionsService
